{"tid":2030362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"524前夕行動 每層都要有連儂牆","createTime":"2020-05-22T16:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T12:44:44.000Z","uid":12629,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ca45d2379544cc8e8ade807fed6336ae9b06cc","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"聽日就係524啦，好可能就係香港人既最後一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但文宣方面既工作似乎仲係好唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係條街起連儂牆又怕比便衣狗捕，藍屍搞<br />\n咁不如我地捨難取易，起啲低風險既連儂牆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係係屋企每層既lip口都痴幾張524文宣</span></strong><br />\n成本低又方便，比人拆咗又易起翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過有幾點要小心！</span><br />\n1. 小心lip口走廊位既cctv<br />\n2. 行動果時先視察情況，睇吓有冇可疑人物<br />\n3. 唔好咁懶淨係痴自己住果幾層，行多幾步痴多幾層，咁對家就無咁易估到你住邊層！<br />\n<br />\n距離524得翻好少時間，各位手足各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fb73ad9f682ef84f17958be4b6a0968b445f2c","tid":2030362,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baad9f3c64cc663756b09c05d56d74292d61dcd6","tid":2030362,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bee02db2e86d8b2716ff1ea59630231cc0e269e","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"我知524仲有好多問題要解決<br />\n但千祈唔好唔記得我哋上年既第一步<br />\n就係打破同溫層，同connect資訊流通唔到既銀髮族<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除咗連儂牆，仲有airdrop文宣</span><br />\n大家做多少少，就成為一個好大嘅力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b7d8dd45087c3a201c9edca8808ee7be1aab84","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"832a79c0f5befc9c01f0e7579d6db9d5c755efff","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9331a01a9fa8ef0e33407b04a2f11fc8d7c64e8","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d110b4398da20b3544b59718dc559581b429a8e","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"572ceb3c69ca1cdbdec39707c8ad1b27e93d9b13","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"ffcb495e7198e64699c7afe53c321a5209d98a6d","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"d0d6307117393c744f169482ea1a6f32dc9d030e","tid":2030362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ad916398c6b97bab62ff45dedf330d9427fd606","tid":2030362,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"4b256ccbc0ac553a24695be0cecc5876d055444c","tid":2030362,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3423a815a0ac5e3d74c039332ba5458b0d7697b4","tid":2030362,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e865a0707a7a87b3dcdf2f836336a469126d4b2","tid":2030362,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:52:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"025838bd056b72226edc8985bc1f8d0bd13ba2f